And now, that's probably what it means.

416
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:14,400
Talk about when you relate yourself to another, that is, relates yourself to what has established the whole relation.

417
00:39:14,719 --> 00:39:23,360
That's the same thing as the phrase, you ground it transparently in the power that constituted the self.

