00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:27,039
These are just two different translations of the same idea.

419
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:34,960
So Jesus, I think you have to think, established this complicated kind of self.

420
00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:41,839
It's like discovering that there's something that you really, really like, but you never noticed you really, really liked it.

421
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:46,160
