00:41:26,679 --> 00:41:28,599
I see, I never turned on the lights back there.

437
00:41:28,599 --> 00:41:31,559
I don't know if it matters, but it makes me happy to have them.

438
00:41:32,119 --> 00:41:39,960
Now, so there are two ways, I think, that you can relate to the God-man.

