458
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:20,880
Now I think there's only one more piece to be put into that.

459
00:43:20,880 --> 00:43:23,520
And that is, how do you relate to Jesus?

460
00:43:23,520 --> 00:43:32,559
What is it to be transparently grounded in that something which established the relation?

461
00:43:32,880 --> 00:43:34,719
And he doesn't even want to say God.

462
00:43:34,719 --> 00:43:37,679
He wants to say something very, very general.

463
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:45,280
But somehow or other, something or other established the self the way it is.

