00:43:55,280 --> 00:44:02,599
Okay, I think that's what he thinks.

472
00:44:02,920 --> 00:44:11,000
If you're a disciple, a contemporary of Jesus, you can have an unconditional relation to Jesus.

473
00:44:11,000 --> 00:44:17,880
