00:44:52,840 --> 00:44:56,679
So that probably is not the way we should be behaving.

482
00:44:56,679 --> 00:45:07,559
Well, Kierkegaard, in the second of the books where he signs them with his highest Christian name, says Jesus is the paradigm.

