00:47:28,280 --> 00:47:47,400
If Jesus is a paradigm, an outstanding example, then he ought to be someone taking a risky unconditional commitment, and maybe it's such a secret sort of underground operation that it doesn't show up very clearly in what the people are writing down, which becomes the New Testament.

509
00:47:47,400 --> 00:47:49,400
I think that would be very interesting.

