00:57:49,440 --> 00:57:53,480
And there's no position again from which to prove who's right.

617
00:57:53,039 --> 00:57:59,799
I believe it.

618
00:58:01,400 --> 00:58:01,960
That's right.

619
00:58:01,960 --> 00:58:03,239
They try to do something.

620
00:58:03,239 --> 00:58:05,960
I mean, I haven't been lectured enough yet by my son.

621
00:58:06,199 --> 00:58:07,240
Give me more time.

622
00:58:07,239 --> 00:58:16,680
But they're trying to do something to do something to the body part, such that they will get some kind of special experience with the other part.

623
00:58:16,679 --> 00:58:18,679
And they think that's what it's all about.

